content.name: The Jungle Club Comedy Lock-In

primaryPhoto.description:
After THE CHOIR OF MAN on Friday and Saturday nights, join us for THE JUNGLE COMEDY LOCK-IN at Arts Theatre!
Starring some of London’s top stand-up comedians, the show runs from 9:45 to 11:00 PM, filling the theatre with late-night laughter. The Jungle stage bar will be open before the show. Whether you’re coming straight from THE CHOIR OF MAN or just for the comedy, you’re in for a treat!
Book your THE JUNGLE COMEDY LOCK-IN theatre tickets with LOVEtheatre today!

Please note: THE JUNGLE COMEDY LOCK-IN requires a separate ticket from THE CHOIR OF MAN. Be sure to purchase your ‘Comedy Lock-In’ ticket if you plan to stay for the comedy after THE CHOIR OF MAN.
